---
date: 2024-09-13
title: "Vanilla Ice Cream No Cook"
tags: ["icecream", "dessert"]
---

### Low -- to 185F

### Ingredients

* 2 C half and half
* 1 C cream
* 156g sugar
* 1/4 t salt
* 57g peach preserves
* 1 T vanilla

### Instructions

1. In sauce pan mix cream and half and half, salt, and peach preserves
2. Slowly bring sauce pan mixture to 185 F
3. Pour mixture into container
4. Cool mixture then mix in 1 T vanilla
5. Store mixture in refrigerator overnight
